t skills. Example Assistant Controller requirements Bachelor's degree required Associate's degree considered with 3+ years' experience Proficiency in Quickbooks Exceptional Microsoft Excel skills Attention to detail Organizational skills Assistant Controller related job titles: Associate Controller Junior Controller Junior Auditor Financial Auditor Senior Controller Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
